---

<section class="section values" aria-label="Why Haven">
  <div class="container section-center">
    <span class="section-label">Why Haven?</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Privacy is on the way out.<br/>Ain't that some sh*t?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">
      Built from the ground up so your conversations are your own'.
    </p>
    <div class="values-grid stagger">
      <!-- Card 1: No data collection -->
      <div class="value-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            <line x1="4.5" y1="4.5" x2="19.5" y2="19.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">We will never collect your data, so we can never sell it</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Haven has no analytics, no tracking, no telemetry. We can't monetize what we don't have.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: E2EE -->
      <div class="value-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">End-to-end encrypted, your data is yours</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Every message is encrypted before it leaves your device. The server only sees encrypted blobs, never plaintext.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Open source -->
      <div class="value-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/>
            <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/>
            <line x1="14" y1="4" x2="10" y2="20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Open source, fully auditable</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Every line of code is public.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/haven-chat-org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="value-link">
          View on GitHub
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/>
            <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: EU hosting -->
      <div class="value-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
            <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Hosted in the EU, outside the Five Eyes</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Our servers run in Germany, outside the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Five_Eyes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="value-inline-link">Five Eyes intelligence alliance</a>. Stronger privacy laws, stronger protection.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 5: No ads -->
      <div class="value-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="2" y1="4" x2="22" y2="20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">No ads, ever</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">Haven will never show you ads. No banners, no sponsored messages, no "promoted" servers. Your attention isn't our product.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 6: No ID required -->
      <div class="value-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <line x1="18" y1="2" x2="22" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="22" y1="2" x2="18" y2="6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">No ID required</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">We'll never ask you to verify your identity. No phone number, no government ID, no face scan. get a beta key via email and go.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
